T1  - Whistle Blowing, Forced CEO Turnover, and Misconduct: The Role of Socially Minded Employees and Directors
AU  - Bereskin, Frederick
AU  - Campbell, Terry
AU  - Kedia, Simi
Y1  - 2019/08/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2020/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2018.3229
