T1  - Age of Decision: Pension Savings Withdrawal and Consumption and Debt Response
AU  - Agarwal, Sumit
AU  - Pan, Jessica
AU  - Qian, Wenlan
Y1  - 2019/06/11
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2020/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2018.3148
